<p>Learning curve is a minor setback with socket, Python 3 Documentations like <a href="https://docs.python.org/3/library/os.html?highlight=os#module-os">OS</a>, <a href="https://docs.python.org/3/library/csv.html?highlight=csv">CSV documentation</a>, the <a href="https://www.tutorialspoint.com/python3/python_networking.htm">python3 networking</a>, and some stack overflow for errors really helped.</p>

